                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="def1-1298-18400406 t18400406-1298-punishment-261"></join>Confined Three Months</rs>.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="largeCaps">BUTTON</hi>—<hi rend="largeCaps">
                     <rs id="t18400406-1298-verdict-2" type="verdictDescription">
                        <interp inst="t18400406-1298-verdict-2" type="verdictCategory" value="notGuilty"></interp>
